Detailed Description

Dynamic structure for unplaying moves.

This class creates a dynamic structure of Unplay_manager's where each Unplay_manager represents one move to be unplayed. When there is played new move, new item of Unplay_node is created appropriate Unplay_manager is filled with actual information and it is stored in the end of the list.
